ntry/2018/12/29/104132"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"WgHY"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6650c258-1cb0-48df-aafe-a5e333700fdd","type":"message","user":"UP6PA1UBE","text":"powerline グリフ入ってないフォントの時に statusline の装飾を落とすとかしたかった","ts":"1613713919.301100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"3O=py"}]},{"client_msg_id":"0ddf8758-948a-41d6-86b8-eb71c13a5224","type":"message","user":"UP6PA1UBE","text":"ないですよね、まあ汎用性を求めないでフォントがなかったらおとなしく自分で入れるのでいいか","ts":"1613713850.300100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"QUd"}]},{"client_msg_id":"17573938-a545-49a7-adf1-caab7edcd159","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"んーそれは難題かも?","ts":"1613711061.296100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"=Te"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f2146dc0-defa-41b8-b745-05fbbd7255e3","type":"message","user":"UP6PA1UBE","text":"gvim で現在適用されてるフォントを調べる方法ありましたっけ？\n`guifont` で複数指定されてるうちのどれが有効になっているか。","ts":"1613710016.295300","thread_ts":"1613710016.295300","reply_count":1,"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"DLREy"}]},{"type":"message","user":"U01NUATHAQ4","text":"\u003c@U01NUATHAQ4\u003e has joined the channel","ts":"1613708288.294200","subtype":"channel_join","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"ea82b6ec-2845-420c-8017-7f40edf2e37c","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"ありがとうございます！これで勝つる","ts":"1613667448.293600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"di/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"4d1012d5-d0ad-43de-8bdf-45529e4bd646","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"あ！いけました！悪さしてる子が他にいました :fearful:","ts":"1613667385.293100","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"tada","count":2,"users":["U9S4G0LJW","U06ECBRTJ"]},{"name":"kzk","count":1,"users":["U9S4G0LJW"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ZL5"}]},{"client_msg_id":"3376f607-622a-4100-8de5-a31db5e4dd46","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"いけますね。自分のコードがどっか悪いのかも","ts":"1613667173.292600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"bXs"}]},{"client_msg_id":"584f7dda-c771-4333-94dc-b2b432c520cc","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"あ、ほんとだ","ts":"1613667162.292300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ewp"}]},{"client_msg_id":"39355e7b-1128-4149-a63e-1e9bb2813035","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"cursor()に変えても同じ","ts":"1613667067.292000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/Kh+I"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a8c50489-202c-4cce-950e-af5b69dff228","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"これの後にC-oで手元だと一発で戻れてるけどなー","ts":"1613666996.291400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"KIoZL"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e8dd1a74-cfb8-4e0a-bb27-7c5b56ca2ee0","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"```e foo.ts\ne bar.ts\ncall setline(1, [1, 2, 3])\nkeepj 2```","ts":"1613666968.290600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"MAX"}]},{"client_msg_id":"fb6c693d-3271-47fb-a4e0-77a8cfa3102f","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"あるぇ","ts":"1613666710.289200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"oCbLz"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f4799253-3646-4579-a8cb-897dbe25954f","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"今のままだとcursorを実行した時にbar.tsの最初に戻るという情報が記録されてしまってるので、これではなくedit時のfoo.tsから飛んできたという情報だけを残せばいけると思う","ts":"1613666704.289000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"8q9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b7f34097-50eb-40ec-9d75-4e4b68c86dfc","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"ありがとうございます\n`execute 'keepjumps call cursor(10, 10)`\nにしても戻らず :cry:","ts":"1613666694.288600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"5ix"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e1ff7b17-82fb-45ce-9ecc-6875db78ac7c","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"cursorの方をkeepjumpsにすると望みの挙動になるはず","ts":"1613666576.286000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"nUEe0"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b76cca58-9455-4438-a607-43f274412fc8","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"Vim script で jumplist について質問です\n• vim でファイルを開く `vim foo.ts`\n• buffer を新規作成する `execute 'edit bar.ts'`\n• `bar.ts` にコードを流し込む `call setline(1, split(l:text, \"\\n\"))`\n• 任意の場所にジャンプする `call cursor(10, 0)` で実現\nでやった時に狙い通りに 10 行目に遷移できたんですが、今度はここから `\u0026lt;C-o\u0026gt;` で元にいたファイル(foo.ts)に戻りたいんですが、\n一旦 bar.ts の 1 行目に戻って、もう一度 `\u0026lt;C-o\u0026gt;` すると `foo.ts` に戻れます。\nこれを 1 行目じゃなくてダイレクトに元いたファイルの場所に戻りたいんですが、いい方法ないでしょうか？\n `edit` した時に jumplist に記録されてしまってると思い、`execute 'keepjumps edit bar.ts'`\nしましたが、記録されてしまいます。何か良い回避策などないでしょうか？","ts":"1613665419.284900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"6ns"}]},{"type":"message","user":"U01NKCTP7B4","text":"\u003c@U01NKCTP7B4\u003e has joined the channel","ts":"1613664149.277300","subtype":"channel_join","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"159db68d-5ff9-4f95-b25a-2bc8931546bb","type":"message","user":"U01BY3SDBRS","text":"ごめんなさい、僕もちょっと勘違いしていたので\nたぶん他の方の言うように `.clang-format` に書く案件ですね","ts":"1613717308.321800","thread_ts":"1613716993.317300","parent_user_id":"U01MYF2N7DM","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"XBXdQ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"9612ac33-e561-4b4d-a0ac-bd0d60f94249","type":"message","user":"U01MYF2N7DM","text":"了解いたしました。ありがとうございます！","ts":"1613717611.323800","thread_ts":"1613716993.317300","parent_user_id":"U01MYF2N7DM","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"pray","count":1,"users":["U01BY3SDBRS"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"b2g"}]}]
